    <item>
      <title>Re: Collsion Update 1/26/05</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=DevCorner&amp;message.id=9531#M9531</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;This seems like a dead thread now, but it's still the best fit for my post, I think...&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Following the 4/12 patch, I've noticed collision and pathfinding in Lavaspinner's Lair has gotten even worse.&amp;nbsp; There have always been&amp;nbsp;issues with the drakes --&amp;nbsp;they fall into the lava sometimes instead of flying across, they get stuck at some points, and the wanderers sometimes move about under the world&amp;nbsp;only to pop up out of the ground when they get aggro --&amp;nbsp;but now the spiders are having issues too.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
